beer.beer_description:
Ever heard of the golden hour? It's that time just before sunset where everything is infused with an amber glow. It's also Beer O'clock.

Deep copper in colour, malt driven with a punchy dose of Centennial & Chinook hops, this easy drinking amber ale is calling your name.
